title: Ultra Chilled Full Collection
description:
10 CDs of downtempo, chill beats, mind expanding music from <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ultra_Records">Ultra Records</a>.

All cleanly IDv3 tagged, all 192kbps VBR or higher.

This is NOT a rar of the original, but the actual MP3s themselves.

Each collection is 2 CDs, in separate folders for each.

Please note:  this is done in &#039;dance mix&#039; style; some songs are bled into one another to allow for a continuous downtempo listening experience.  If you are looking for &#039;singles&#039; of many of these songs, please check elsewhere, as you most likely won&#039;t appreciate that there are bits of other songs at the beginning and/or end of the single you are looking for.
